GSD.description:
ethernet: aeroflex: fix potential skb leak in greth_init_rings()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.4.227 by commit 99669d94ce145389f1d6f197e6e18ed50d43fb76, it was introduced in version v2.6.34 by commit d4c41139df6e74c6fff0cbac43e51cab782133be. For more details please see the references link.
